./sample_pp.pl -name "sample1" -trainsize 500 -testsize 100

will make a directroy "sample1" 
will randomly pick 500 examples from the 20801 example training set and randomly select 20 examples form the 4039 development set.

Accuracy evaluated to standard output.

Detailed output of each iteration goes to sample1/detailed_output
Final labels of the test examples are in sample1/out.long, incorrect predictions are marked with "X" at beginning of the line.
Note that when training size is small the results may differ a lot.
